features: 【FUN TIMES STRAIGHT AHEAD】Help your kids set their designs in motion with our brand new cars set! Our magnetic set of cars allow little ones to use their imagination to create fun, mobile designs! The possibilities are limitless – they can even connect their cars to form a train! With this amazing magnetic train set, your child will be able to experience a whole new way to use their mag tiles!

【COMPATIBLE WITH MAJOR BRANDS】Necessarily, Coodoo magnetic blocks are compatible with major brands in markets. You can extend your existing magnetic blocks set by adding more building tiles. This time, Coodoo magnetic blocks with stainless steel security and stronger magnets will be a safer and more reliable option for you to consider.

【STEM LEARNING】 Besides being appropriate for both indoor and outdoor activities, this Magnetic Blocks set is also a highly regarded educational resource. Children can develop math, science, spatial, and tactile skills while learning how to problem-solve and work as a part of a team. Suitable for ages three and up.

【LEARNING WITH CREATIVE FUN】 In today’s world, we are all looking for ways to educate our children and keep them busy. Why not accomplish both with an educational and hands-on magnetic construction toy set that allows them to express their inner creativity? We Encourage Children to Be the Makers of Their Own Worlds. Anything they can dream, they can create!

【GIVE THE GIFT OF FUN & LEARNING】 Coodoo’ magnet tile blocks make the perfect present for friends and family! Whether they’re just getting started on their magnetic block set, or they’re adding new pieces, birthday boys and girls are guaranteed to love our new car play set.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Hit hit hit! ❤️
reviews.reviewText: This toy was the hit for Christmas! Got a kit for my daughter and another one for my nephew! reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Will definitely be buying more
reviews.reviewText: The little guy that I bought these for I have cared for while his Mama worked since he was 2 years old And he just turned 5 so I know we were ready for something different from Legos which I had noticed he was getting bored with the legos So when I seen these I went straight to research and review mode and Man am I glad I did because he absolutely LOVED them! I’m looking now to see how much more I can get to make his collection even bigger He said he want to build Elsa’s Castle 🥰 I absolutely love this little guy….Parents you won’t regret it and there’s not teeny tiny pieces you have to worry about It’s a Must Buy in my opinion

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought these to add to our collection of magna tiles to be able to build more and bigger things. I was struggling to find a set I could use with an older style tile I have that is 5 or so years old. These do work with my original set so that’s a huge plus! The set is smaller than I thought but hopefully using the 2 sets we can build bigger and better things! My 2 year old, 7 yr old, my husband , and myself love magna tiles!😊
